By the second week, the initial measurments will be complete, the hand mold started, and the wiring and intial code will be started and a test run complete
by the third week the finger molds will be started and the hand mold finished, the wiring will progress to two servos
by the fourth week the box will be designed and the CAD assembly will be started, the code will be near completion
by the fifth week the irl assembly will be started and the code complete, test runs will procede
by the sixth week the assembly will be completed, code completed with full test runs, project done.
            give or take a week or two: projected time being 6-8 weeks
